      "comboUsage": "",
      "strategicPurpose": "",
      "iconName": "Duality",
      "tips": "As we've said many times already, Luo Yi's skills take advantage of a \"Yin\" and \"Yang\" mechanic. Whenever two enemy heroes inflicted with opposite marks come close to each other, a \"Yin Yang Reaction\"will be triggered, causing them to collide with each other which deals damage, while stunning them. Also, whenever a \"Yin Yang Reaction\" occurs, Luo Yi will gain a slight shield and movement speed boost .",
      "iconUrl": "/raw-assets/skill_icons/luoyi/duality.png",
      "displayLabel": "Passive",
      "skillSlot": "passive"
    },
