      "iconName": "Dispersion",
      "tips": "Luo Yi casts Yin or Yang energy wave in a designated direction, alternating between the two opposing energy types between each cast. The energy will disperse upon hitting the first target, dealing damage to the first target and any enemies behind them in a fan shaped area. The energy wave also inflicts an Yin or Yang Mark on any enemy heroes upon contact. Luo Yi's first skill is her primary damage dealing skill. Additionally, this skill is the primary way to trigger Yin Yang Reactions.",
